mil.nga.giat.geowave.store.index

Interface CommonIndexModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataReader<CommonIndexValue>, DataWriter<Object,CommonIndexValue>, Persistable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicIndexModel

    public interface CommonIndexModel
extends DataReader<CommonIndexValue>, DataWriter<Object,CommonIndexValue>, Persistable
    This interface describes the common fields for all of the data within the index. It is up to data adapters to map (encode) the native fields to these common fields for persistence.
